<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another point here is that the chronic bad new=
s makes it hard to find a permanent solution. The basic state of First Repu=
blic is that its assets are worth less than its liabilities,=C2=A0<em>as an=
 economic matter</em>, but it is well capitalized=C2=A0<em>as a regulatory =
capital matter</em>. This means that it can limp along indefinitely, but no=
body wants to buy it because the correct price for it is negative.<a class=
=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-6" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
